data.description: Welcome to 122 S 6th Ave, a charming and spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home situated on a picturesque 3/4 acre lot in Sterling, OK! This beautiful property presents an incredible opportunity to embrace the serene country living while still being conveniently located near city amenities. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating an ideal space for entertaining and hosting family gatherings. The chef in your family will appreciate the well-appointed kitchen, showcasing newly purchased modern appliances, ample cabinetry, and a convenient breakfast bar. Retreat to the private primary bedroom, offering a tranquil oasis with an en-suite bathroom for ultimate relaxation. Additionally, two generously sized bedrooms with ample closet space and a full bathroom complete the interior of this delightful home. Outside, your expansive backyard provides endless possibilities. Picture summer barbecues, gardening, or even adding a pool to create your own personal oasis. The vast 3/4 acre lot grants plenty of space for kids and pets to run and play freely, offering a truly peaceful and private setting. Conveniently located in the charming town of Sterling, this property provides easy access to local schools, parks, and amenities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this inviting and well-maintained residence your dream home. Call or text listing agent now to schedule your private showing! Carrie Austin, NextHome Tri-Covenant Realty, (580) 512-6647
